# Simon Says Game ðŸŽ®

This is a simple memory game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## How to Play
- Press any key to start.
- Watch the color sequence.
- Click buttons in the same order.
- Game ends when you click the wrong button.

## Features
- Level tracking
- Random color sequence
- Game over screen with score

